---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Give to Church Planting in India — Church Planting Movement"
  description="Support the church planting movement in India. Your gift empowers indigenous pastors to plant new churches among unreached people groups."
  keywords="give to church planting India, church planting movement India, support Christian missionaries India, unreached people India, advancing the gospel in India"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "DonateAction",
      "name": "Give to Church Planting in India",
      "description": "Support the church planting movement in India. Empower indigenous pastors to plant new churches among unreached people groups.",
      "recipient": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Global Hope India", "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org" },
      "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org/give/church-planting"
    })}></script>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] lg:min-h-[60vh] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1D1C1C]" style="background-image:url('https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/images/ghi-201811_globalhopeindia_church-56-scaled.jpg');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 via-black/30 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pb-12 pt-40">
      <p class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Church Planting</p>
      <h1 style="color:white!important;" class="max-w-3xl font-bold text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[50px] leading-[1.2]">Give to Church Planting<br/>in India</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/70 text-lg max-w-xl">Empower indigenous pastors to start new churches among India's most unreached people groups.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IMPACT STATS -->
  <section class="bg-[#2EAB5A] py-10 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center text-white">
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">$150</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">1 month pastor support</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">12</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Church-planting partners</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">139</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Mission teams sent</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">25+</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Years of ministry</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Church Planting in India?</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
            <p>India has more <strong>unreached people groups</strong> than almost any country on earth. Hundreds of millions of Indians live in communities where there is no church, no pastor, and no Christian witness.</p>
            <p>The most effective strategy for advancing the gospel in India is through <strong>indigenous church planting</strong>. Indian pastors understand the language, culture, and needs of their communities far better than any outside missionary ever could.</p>
            <p>When you give to church planting in India, you empower local pastors with the training, resources, and support they need to start healthy, reproducing churches. These churches become the launching point for Bible distribution, orphan care, community development, and the discipleship of new believers.</p>
            <p>Global Hope India partners with <strong>12 indigenous church-planting leaders</strong> across North, South, East, and Northeast India. Your gift of <strong>$150 supports a church planter for one month</strong> — paying for travel, materials, and family provision so they can focus entirely on building God's kingdom.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="bg-[#F8F5EF] rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-xl font-bold mb-4">Support a Church Planter</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555] text-sm mb-6">Your gift goes directly to empowering indigenous pastors who are advancing the gospel among unreached people in India.</p>
            <a href="https://givebutter.com/GlobalHopeIndia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-[#06038D] hover:bg-[#1D1C1C] text-white font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md w-full">Donate Now</a>
            <p class="text-[#666] text-xs mt-4 font-medium">Over 85% of every dollar goes directly to programs in India.</p>
            <p class="text-[#999] text-xs mt-1">Global Hope India is a 501(c)(3). All gifts are tax-deductible.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-4">
              <img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/r33r2z1j/production/767b76c41ccc43b3c07f07c94435a4dcc3ad13b3-500x500.svg" alt="GuideStar Platinum Seal" width="32" height="32" loading="lazy" class="h-8 opacity-70" />
              <img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/r33r2z1j/production/07b08d8f4d9321bb85fa7814ef0d65a742b3463e-500x500.png" alt="Charity Navigator 100" width="32" height="32" loading="lazy" class="h-8 opacity-70" />
              <img src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/r33r2z1j/production/f256d3af6f9dbfbc282103b8fb3f7037a98d64db-500x500.png" alt="Better Business Bureau" width="32" height="32" loading="lazy" class="h-8 opacity-70" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 bg-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Your Gift at Work</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555]">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">$150</span> — Support a church planter for 1 month</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">$450</span> — Support a church planter for 3 months</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">$900</span> — Support a church planter for 6 months</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">$1,800</span> — Support a church planter for 1 year</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-[#2EAB5A] text-center py-12 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-[26px] md:text-[36px] mb-4">Build God's Kingdom in India</h2>
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">Every new church is a beacon of hope in a community that has never heard the gospel. Give to the church planting movement in India today.</p>
      <a href="https://givebutter.com/GlobalHopeIndia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-white hover:bg-stone-100 text-[#2EAB5A] font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md">Give to Church Planting</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
